<!-- Modal Artist -->
<div class="modal fade" id="modal_artist" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-custom" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header-custom  d-flex align-items-center justify-content-end">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="text-body">
          <div class="body-title">
            <h1 class="title text-center">Artique For Artists</h1>
            <br>
            <h2 class="color c-blue modal-lead-text">Artyque for Artists is a new kind of service that allies the expertise of an agent with the power of connection only a digital platform can provide.</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="container-fluid separate-content-bottom">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12 col-sm-6">Acting on your behalf and only in your interest, we negotiate, organise and promote your exhibitions across Europe, find fundings for your projects, develop your provenance and ultimately increase the value of your works. 
              <br><br><b class="color c-blue">Your only task will be creating your next masterpiece.</b></div>
              <div class="col-12 col-sm-6"> 
                After signing with us you will get a personal agent and access to our platform on which you will develop your profile and digital portfolio. We will then work our magic while you enjoy a stress-free creation process back to your studio. </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container-bullets">
         <div class="w-100 wrapper-body-bullets background bg-blue">
          <ul>
            <li> Promote your portfolio to galleries and art institutions that fit your talent</li> 
            <li> Organise new shows of your works in Europe</li> 
            <li> Increase your press visibility</li> 
            <li> Connect you with collectors and patrons</li> 
            <li> Support your career growth </li> 
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
       <div class="text-body text-center separate-content">
          <div class="body-title">
            <h1 class="title text-center">Artique For Artists</h1>
            <h2 class="color c-blue modal-lead-text">Places are limited. </h2>
          </div>
          <div class="form-set">
              <%= render 'contact_forms/new' %>
           </div> 
        </div> 
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

